{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1976,"month":5,"day":15}],"page_start":3,"page_end":3,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"毛主席光辉照黎家","authors":["李风光（黎族）"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"是什么风吹得漫山遍野翠绿？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是什么雨浇得大地盛开百花？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，映入眼帘的是一幅什么画卷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"页页描绘着祖国江山的金彩霞？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬一杯爽口香甜的椰子水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"献一朵世上稀有的木棉花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捧一把大寨田里的新良种，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"采一担黎寨的开春茶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱黎族人的心意献出来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们用优美的歌声作回答——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是文化革命的春雨洒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才有五指山上的遍地花！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是毛主席的光辉照黎家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才有我们黎族人的好年华！"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}